    "body": "Anyone can propose a feature. Of course, you can't force others to use it, but good proposals will be used if there is a need for it.\n\nI am not sure how to best allocate a feature number. As I wrote in the proposal, a random 64 bit number could be used. This is maybe not a safe process, as you could claim that you got the number '1' as a random. Another way is to use a hash, but hash on what?\n\nI am thinking a little like you allocate a new account address. You don't need a central control of what addresses are allocated.\n",
